<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Riggors Mortus</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-06 10:49:23</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The warlord walks around a lot.  I usually find him near the main door or walking on the left or right of it (outside).<BR>
<BR>
The BoB comes up 1 in every 5-6 drops I'd say.<BR>
<BR>
Hard to hunt since he roams a lot.  People say they are camping him but he is a roamer so I don't think you can really camp him, just gotta be lucky to find him.  I walk by him and if he hits me he's mine (as long as he has no damage or DOTs on him  -  heheeh).<BR>
<BR>
My experience is he's outside 4 out of 5 times (and by himself).  People jump him quick so grab him quick and give a friendly shout that he is yours.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck!  I've outgrown Crushbones so I prob won't be seeing him at all.<BR>
<BR>
Riggors Mortus<BR>
27th Lvl Paladin</font></td></tr></table>
